sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client / KServe
    participant API as ModelMeshApi<br/>8033/TCP gRPC<br/>TLS + mTLS (optional)
    participant Mesh as SidecarModelMesh<br/>(Local Instance)
    participant Runtime as Model Runtime<br/>8085/TCP or UDS<br/>gRPC plaintext
    participant RemoteMesh as Remote ModelMesh<br/>8080/TCP Thrift<br/>TLS (optional)
    participant RemoteRT as Remote Runtime<br/>8085/TCP or UDS<br/>gRPC plaintext
    participant etcd as etcd<br/>2379/TCP gRPC<br/>TLS (configurable)

    Note over Client,etcd: Flow 1: Model Inference Request (Cache Hit)
    Client->>API: gRPC inference RPC<br/>TLS + mTLS (optional)
    API->>Mesh: Java method call (in-process)
    Mesh->>Mesh: Check local model cache
    alt Model loaded locally (cache hit)
        Mesh->>Runtime: gRPC inference forward<br/>plaintext (localhost)
        Runtime-->>Mesh: Inference result
    else Model on remote instance (cache miss)
        Mesh->>RemoteMesh: Thrift (Litelinks) forward<br/>TLS + mTLS (optional)
        RemoteMesh->>RemoteRT: gRPC inference forward<br/>plaintext (localhost)
        RemoteRT-->>RemoteMesh: Inference result
        RemoteMesh-->>Mesh: Inference result
    end
    Mesh-->>API: Response
    API-->>Client: gRPC response

    Note over Client,etcd: Flow 2: Model Registration and Loading
    Client->>API: registerModel RPC<br/>TLS + mTLS (optional)
    API->>Mesh: Register model (in-process)
    Mesh->>etcd: Create ModelRecord<br/>gRPC TLS (configurable)
    etcd-->>Mesh: Confirm write
    Mesh->>Mesh: Select instance for loading<br/>(capacity, constraints, balancing)
    Mesh->>Runtime: loadModel RPC<br/>gRPC plaintext (localhost)
    Runtime-->>Mesh: Model loaded (size, metadata)
    Mesh->>etcd: Update ModelRecord status<br/>→ LOADED
    etcd-->>Mesh: Confirm update
    Mesh-->>API: Registration result
    API-->>Client: Model registered + status

    Note over Client,etcd: Flow 3: Virtual Model Transition (Zero-Downtime)
    Client->>API: setVModel RPC<br/>(vmodel_id, target_model_id)
    API->>Mesh: Set vmodel (in-process)
    Mesh->>etcd: Create/update VModelRecord<br/>gRPC TLS (configurable)
    etcd-->>Mesh: Confirm write
    Mesh->>Mesh: VModelManager: ensureLoaded<br/>for target model
    Mesh->>Runtime: loadModel (target)<br/>gRPC plaintext (localhost)
    Runtime-->>Mesh: Target model loaded
    Mesh->>etcd: Atomic swap:<br/>active ↔ target model
    etcd-->>Mesh: Swap confirmed
    Mesh-->>API: VModel transition complete
    API-->>Client: VModel updated
